originalText: Can't you hit any harder, meatbag?
You cannot even get to the meat.
I'll make you bleed for this!
AAARGH! I can't feel my arm!
Argh! That's gonna leave a big scar...
Arrrgh... pain is good... pain is good..
::Gasps for air.:: You knocked... my... air... out...
Ugh... I think that broke something...
Damn it, you hit hard, meatbag...
I'll tear you limb from limb for this...
I can't... move... I... I... Hnnnn...
I feel... it... in... my... b-bones...
Where the hell are you!? I'll... I'll...
My brain is being crushed! Ugggh!
I'll gouge your eyes out with this bolt.
AAAAAARRGH! I can see the bone!
Stop, drop, roll... STOP, DROP, ROLL!
It's burning me! Make it stop! Arrrgh!
Put it out! Put it out!
::Frantically tries to pat the fire out.::
I'll kill you... I'll *eat* you ALL!
I'm not ready... I'm not ready yet...
I think my rib is broken...
No! Get out... GET OUT OF MY... HEEEEEAAAAD!
Oh, you won't have me. You! Won't! Have! Meeeee-heheh!
Brrrr! Grrrr! There is someone else in my... my... mind! Aaargh!
Precious lifeblood, gotta stop the flow...
I'll be making weapons from your bones.
I will chop off little pieces of you and make you eat them.
Please, stay for dinner. I insist.
Worry not, all your parts will be put to good use.
Death is but the beginning. You blood will sustain my life.
Like a hopper to a slaughter.
It's time to give up, prey...
Do not worry. Through us, you'll live on.
I can almost taste your flesh...
Nice and crispy. Just the way I like it.
Where do you think you're going, prey?
Come on, you're not gonna sleep now, are you?
Wake up, I'm not done with you yet!
Don't worry, we'll drain the poison from your meat.
Feeling sick? No sense in worrying about your health anymore.
Mmm... I can smell your blood.
Give up, you're not a hunter. You are prey.
Oh, yes... I'm back in action!
Yeah, bring me the sweet meat!
I'll beat you to a bloody pulp!
It's time to tenderize the meat.
I'll carve you up like a mushroom cake!
Let's put a bloody smile on that face!
This bullet's got your name on it!
Can you feel the energy, little hopper?
Don't worry, it'll be quick and very painful...
Welcome to the green side of life...
I'll turn you into red swill!
How about a napalm shower, meatbag!?
See if you can catch this!
I'll pin you to a wall!
I've got the bolt just for you!
A battle of the minds incoming!
I'll turn your brain to mush!
Now you see me, now you don't.
I don't know why, but the word "hypothermia" just springs to my mind...
Chilled bones are easier to break!
I hope you're wearing something warm.
You are gonna be so cool. ::Grins.::
How about I burn that smile off your face!?
Let's heat things up a bit...
You're gonna be on fire, little hopper!
No one will be able to fix ya after I'm done with you!
We got some raw meat here!
I need some help over here!
The moment of your doom has arrived!
I do like skewered meat... greatly!
I'll turn you into minced meat!
I'll blow your head open... and scoop up what's inside!
We don't need your kind here!
